The Toll Brothers Advantage | Toll Brothers® Luxury Homes






































































Toll Brothers  - America's Luxury Home Builder







The Toll Brothers Advantage






Choose Toll Brothers and experience the advantage of our award-winning designs, hundreds of personalization options, the highest-quality building products, and our environmentally sensitive building methods – all in the best locations across the country. Explore the Toll Brothers Advantage.


Best Locations

The best locations in the nation.
At Toll Brothers, we believe that lifestyle has everything to do with where you live. That's why we select only the best locations across the nation. We take everything into consideration: scenic views, access to natural amenities, proximity to schools and commuter routes, nearby entertainment, and much more. The end result is a community of luxury homes with outstanding amenities, gorgeous surroundings, and a convenient location.
We're currently building communities in 20 states: Arizona, California, Colorado, Connecticut, Delaware, Florida, Idaho, Illinois, Maryland, Massachusetts, Michigan, Minnesota, Nevada, New Jersey, New York, North Carolina, Pennsylvania, Texas, Virginia, and Washington.



Personalization Options

Your home should be truly yours.
Your home is a reflection of you. We believe that a truly personalized lifestyle starts with your unique home design decisions. That's why we offer personalization opportunities and tools such as our Design Your Own Home tool – it allows you to lead the design process for your dream home. Start building your dream home by browsing nearly 500 design options including sunrooms, greenhouses, in-law suites, and much more.
Personalize every detail.
We've teamed up with the most talented design consultants around the country to create the Toll Brothers Design Studios, available in 23 centralized locations across the country. We guide you through vignettes of complete rooms for inspiration, then provide one-on-one guidance to help you compare and select everything from flooring and lighting to kitchen and bath products to home automation.
The result is a Toll Brothers home designed by you, for you.



Superior Architectural Design

Award-winning architectural design.
At Toll Brothers, we provide what matters most: the highest quality construction and superior architectural design from a builder you can trust. To ensure tight quality control for every home we build, we developed Toll Architecture, our in-house architectural firm that ensures uncompromising standards of design.
Our team at Toll Architecture develops award-winning designs that are the soul of a Toll Brothers home. We offer an extensive variety of floor plan layouts and design options so that you can make your house your own. The result is a wide and varied palette of unique, exciting homes with many special features – including dramatic butterfly staircases, luxurious master bathrooms, elaborate gourmet kitchens, and much more.
To further explore our award winning designs, visit our Design Center.



Top Brand Products

Premium products in every home.
Every Toll Brothers home is appointed with the highest-quality brand-name products in the industry.  We partner with high-end manufacturers and leverage our national purchasing power to bring greater quality and value to your home. From appliances and flooring products to cabinetry and plumbing fixtures, we're proud to build luxury homes featuring these outstanding brands:

American Olean: Stunning porcelain, glass, and stone floor and wall tiles
Andersen: Beautiful, energy-efficient windows and doors
Armstrong: Flooring designs ranging from hardwood to luxury vinyl to laminate
Baldwin: Meticulously crafted door hardware, luxury cabinet hardware, bath accessories, and locks
Bosch: Efficient home appliances in sleek designs
Bose: The finest quality home theater and stereo systems
Carrier: Energy efficient home heating, cooling, and indoor air quality products
Certainteed: Vinyl siding, fence, decking, interior insulation, and ceiling products
Clopay: Beautiful, quiet, and durable garage and entry doors
Control4: Home automation solutions for integrating lighting, music, climate control, and your mobile devices
Daltile: Innovative tile and stone products for stylish kitchen, bath and interior designs
Dupont Corian: Virtually seamless solid-surface material for stunning bathroom and kitchen countertops and backsplashes
GAF: High quality, attractive shingles designed to withstand the test of time
Heat & Glo: Ambiance and warmth, inside and out, from fireplaces, gas stoves/fireplaces
Heatilator: Gas and electric fireplaces and other indoor/outdoor fireplace and heart products
Honeywell: Peace of mind and home protection with home automation security and surveillance systems
JamesHardie: Superior siding products including HardiePlank® and HardieShingle® siding solutions
Jenn-Air: From refrigerators to outdoor grills, Jenn-Air is a leader in luxury kitchen appliances
Johns Manville: Efficient and cost-effective home insulation solutions
Kitchenaid: High-performance kitchen appliances in a variety of designs
Kohler: High-end, designer quality kitchen and bath fixtures
Liftmaster: Garage doors offering the latest designs and innovative technology
Masonite: Beautiful, impressive, and durable interior, entry, and patio doors
Miele: Sophisticated  appliances with timeless looks and optimum performance and efficiency
Mohawk: Flooring solutions ranging from stain-resistant carpet to engineered hardwood
Nutone: Residential ventilation solutions ranging from bath fans to range hoods
OwensCorning: Comfortable and energy efficient insulation products
Progress Lighting: Efficient and beautiful interior and exterior lighting designs
Shaw Floors: A leader in superior quality and design flooring products, from carpet to hardwood to laminate
Sherwin-Williams: Paints, stains, and other coating supplies
Sub-Zero and Wolf: Extraordinary professional-grade kitchen appliances
Thermador: Award winning cooking, cleaning, and refrigeration appliances
Timberlake Cabinetry: Stylish, high-quality kitchen and bathroom cabinets
Velux: Skylights and sun tunnels to brighten your home with natural sunlight
Viking: High-quality ranges, cooktops, refrigerators, and wine cellar products
Wayne Dalton: Designer wood, steel, fiberglass, and other contemporary garage doors
Whirlpool: Appliances for the kitchen and laundry room by a leader in high-performing appliances
Yorktowne Cabinetry: Fine craftsmanship and luxurious cabinetry products

These brands are listed as a representative sample only and may not be available for purchase at all communities.  Please consult  with a Toll Brothers' sales representative for specific information on availability and pricing.




Building Green
Honoring our environment, inside and out.
At Toll Brothers, we care about our environment. Preserving our natural environment is an integral part of creating a community. It's why we created Toll Green, which is committed to:

Building energy-efficient homes that reduce our environmental impact. From energy efficient gas furnaces to engineered wood flooring, we integrate green features into every home. You can make your home even more environmentally friendly by customizing it with a wide variety of sustainable products.
Building homes that harmonize with the beauty of the natural landscape. We preserve as much open space as possible, incorporating and even restoring the existing hills, trees, and ponds.







 



